textBody:
Limerick is a city in Ireland.

It may also refer to:
* Limerick (poetry)
* Limerick (song)

;Ireland
*County Limerick
*Limerick, a city in County Limerick

*Limerick Township, Pennsylvania
**Limerick Nuclear Power Plant

;1801–1885
*Limerick City (UK Parliament constituency)
*County Limerick (UK Parliament constituency)
;1885–1922
*Limerick City (UK Parliament constituency)

*West Limerick (UK Parliament constituency)
;1921–1923
*Kerry–Limerick West (Dáil Éireann constituency)
*Limerick City–Limerick East (Dáil Éireann constituency)

;1948–
*Limerick East (Dáil Éireann constituency)
*Limerick West (Dáil Éireann constituency)

People

*Patricia Nelson Limerick, an American historian
*Earl of Limerick, a British noble title

Other

*Limerick lace, a variety of needle lace
*Limerick F.C., an Irish soccer team
